
.styleguide-h3 Flags
.styleguide-quarter
  %p Flags are used to <span class="flag important">pop</span> information in a <code>block</code> of text, they are generally used with <code>inline</code> elements.
.styleguide-threequarter.indent
  %table(cellspacing="0")
    %thead
      %tr
        %th Flag
        %th Markup
    %tbody
      %tr
        %td <span class="flag">Standard</span>
        %td <code>&lt;span class="flag"&gt;Standard&lt;/span&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <span class="flag notice">Notice</span>
        %td <code>&lt;span class="flag notice"&gt;Notice&lt;/span&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <span class="flag important">Important</span>
        %td <code>&lt;span class="flag important"&gt;Important&lt;/span&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <span class="flag success">Success</span>
        %td <code>&lt;span class="flag success"&gt;Success&lt;/span&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <span class="flag warning">Warning</span>
        %td <code>&lt;span class="flag warning"&gt;Warning&lt;/span&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <span class="flag alert">Alert</span>
        %td <code>&lt;span class="flag alert"&gt;Alert&lt;/span&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <span class="flag error">Error</span>
        %td <code>&lt;span class="flag error"&gt;Error&lt;/span&gt;</code>
.styleguide-clearfix

.styleguide-h3 Stickers
.styleguide-quarter
  %p Stickers are similar to flags, except they are generally wrapped around <code>block</code> or <code>inline-block</code> level elements such as <code>headings</code>. Stickers add <code>display: inline-block</code> to their elements.
.styleguide-threequarter.indent
  %table(cellspacing="0")
    %thead
      %tr
        %th Sticker
        %th Markup
    %tbody
      %tr
        %td <h4 class="sticker">Standard</h4>
        %td <code>&lt;h4 class="sticker"&gt;Standard&lt;/h4&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <h4 class="sticker notice">Notice</h4>
        %td <code>&lt;h4 class="sticker notice"&gt;Notice&lt;/h4&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <h4 class="sticker important">Important</h4>
        %td <code>&lt;h4 class="sticker important"&gt;Important&lt;/h4&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <h4 class="sticker success">Success</h4>
        %td <code>&lt;h4 class="sticker success"&gt;Success&lt;/h4&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <h4 class="sticker warning">Warning</h4>
        %td <code>&lt;h4 class="sticker warning"&gt;Warning&lt;/h4&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <h4 class="sticker alert">Alert</h4>
        %td <code>&lt;h4 class="sticker alert"&gt;Alert&lt;/h4&gt;</code>
      %tr
        %td <h4 class="sticker error">Error</h4>
        %td <code>&lt;h4 class="sticker error"&gt;Error&lt;/h4&gt;</code>
.styleguide-clearfix


.styleguide-h3 Buttons
